WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
To use the chat function in a meeting,

2
00:00:07.100 --> 00:00:11.000
click on the show conversation button
in the meeting controls.

3
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:14.000
This will make the 
meeting chat panel slide out.

4
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:17.000
To format text,
click on the format button.

5
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:21.000
Here you have the options to bold, 
italicise, underline, 

6
00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:26.000
strike through and highlight text.
As well as change the font colour.

7
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:31.000
The more options button has
more text formatting options.

8
00:00:31.100 --> 00:00:34.000
The chat box has a lot of
different options,

9
00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:37.000
including the ability 
to share a YouTube video.

10
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:40.000
The options for the meeting chat are  
the same as those available...

11
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:42.000
...in the chat tab.
